# HallederizCRM Premium - Project Context

This repository is a Turkish CRM and operations platform.

Core product areas:
- CRM / cari management
- Orders
- Payments / tahsilat
- Stock and inventory
- WhatsApp operations
- Approvals
- Documents
- Reports
- AI-assisted operation planning

Before making UI changes, read these files:

- crm-ui-blueprint.md
- crm-backlog.md
- cursor-screen-prompt.md
- reference-dashboard-v1.png

Current UI priority:

1. App shell
2. Sidebar
3. Topbar
4. Dashboard homepage
5. Toast and modal system
6. Archive page
7. Other pages

Use Turkish labels for user-facing UI.

Do not create a separate AI item in the left sidebar.
AI Assistant appears only on the dashboard homepage.
AI settings belong under Ayarlar.
